pageContext.claim: “I read Mitch McConnell's statement yesterday, and he read my phone call. And, as you know, he put out a statement that said that was the most innocent phone call he's read.”
pageContext.analysis: McConnell said the readout of the July 25 phone call between Trump and the Ukrainian president did not raise an impeachable offense, but he did not say it was "the most innocent phone call."
